OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777551071
OL,3,CMan sentenced for stealing 24-tonne
OL,4,Cdigger and driving it through
OL,5,CWolverhampton
OL,7,FThis was the moment onlookers watched
OL,8,Fin shock as Darren Coffey drove the
OL,9,Fstolen bulldozer through Wolverhampton
OL,11,FA man has been sentenced after
OL,12,Fstealing a 24-tonne-bulldozer and
OL,13,Fdriving it through Wolverhampton city
OL,14,Fcentre.
OL,16,F41-year-old Darren Coffey was
OL,17,Fsentenced to 18 months in prison at
OL,18,FWolverhampton Crown Court after he
OL,19,Fdrove the bulldozer through the city
OL,20,Fcentre and smashed into a Royal Mail
OL,21,Florry last November.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
