FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777551071
OL,3,CMan sentenced for stealing 24-tonne
OL,4,Cdigger and driving it through
OL,5,CWolverhampton
OL,7,FHe was sentenced for dangerous driving
OL,8,Fand threatening to destroy property,
OL,9,Fwith no separate penalty for the other
OL,10,Foffences.
OL,12,FCoffey previously pleaded guilty to
OL,13,Fnine charges, including dangerous
OL,14,Fdriving, criminal damage, drink
OL,15,Fdriving and threatening to destroy
OL,16,Fproperty.
OL,18,FThe court was told that the D6
OL,19,Fcaterpillar digger was worth #385,000,
OL,20,Fand was taken from an address in
OL,21,FStaffordshire on November 8 2025.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777551071
OL,3,CMan sentenced for stealing 24-tonne
OL,4,Cdigger and driving it through
OL,5,CWolverhampton
OL,7,FThe 41-year-old from Sandwell, removed
OL,8,Fthe vehicles tracker in the process
OL,9,Fand drove it through Wolverhampton in
OL,10,Fa bid to target a business with which
OL,11,Fhe was in an ongoing civil dispute.
OL,13,FThe court heard how Coffey called West
OL,14,FMidlands Police stating he wanted to
OL,15,Fburn down Willenhall Motors, and said
OL,16,Fhe was "heading there with two petrol
OL,17,Fcans".
OL,19,FAs well as failing to stop, the judge
OL,20,Fsaid Coffey damaged various items of
OL,21,Fstreet furniture.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777551071
OL,3,CMan sentenced for stealing 24-tonne
OL,4,Cdigger and driving it through
OL,5,CWolverhampton
OL,7,FJudge Perry said the offences were too
OL,8,Fserious for a community order.
OL,10,F"You do represent a risk, and in my
OL,11,Fview the seriousness of the offence
OL,12,Fmeans that the only appropriate
OL,13,Fpunishment can be immediate custody,
OL,14,FI'm going to have to send you to
OL,15,Fprison today.
OL,17,F"From the video footage I've seen,
OL,18,Fit's fair to say (you) caused untold
OL,19,Fchaos to the road users.
OL,26,@zD@RpmzD@Vpn
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
