OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777551071
OL,3,CMan sentenced for stealing 24-tonne
OL,4,Cdigger and driving it through
OL,5,CWolverhampton
OL,7,FHe added, "You reversed into oncoming
OL,8,Ftraffic, and on one occasion that
OL,9,Fincluded police cars. The effect of
OL,10,Fthat on normal road users is
OL,11,Fdemonstrated from the expletives
OL,12,Freacted by the police officers."
OL,14,FCoffey has also been banned from
OL,15,Fdriving for three years and will need
OL,16,Fto do an extended retest before he can
OL,17,Fdrive again.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
